    <div class="o-width about wc-50">
        <div class="o-text-field two-columns">

            <div class="headings" style="text-align:left;">
                <div class="m-headline">
                    <span class="heading-cap">Recipe</span>
                    This vegan salad is a summertime favourite in ARKET cafés. Starring sweet,
                    juicy tomatoes that are at their best this time of the year, it is packed with vitamins and minerals.
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="text-container">
                <p class="a-paragraph is-richtext">
                    The hearty hummus base, tahini-flavoured legumes and roasted bell peppers make for a satisfying meal,
                    yet the salad is light enough to serve on a hot day. Our fresh tomato dressing adds a finishing zing
                    and will pair beautifully with other seasonal salads and grilled dishes. Try the salad at home or enjoy it on a summer-loving picnic with family and friends.
                    To make it gluten-free, skip the croutons or replace them with a gluten-free alternative.
                </p>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>

